channel.title: RS Browse
channel.description:
Hi,
I have just finished creating a simple runescape world switcher, it uses basic html with a very small amount of javascript. You will need a browser with frames support.
[url=http://www.livealittle.me.uk/rs]Open RS Browse (click here)[/url]
If you have any comments or suggestions please feel free to post here, PM me on this forum or E-Mail me at takeabow@wasteurlife.com
This is [b][u]NOT[/u][/b] a keylogger or any other way designed to steal your RuneScape Password.
